{"tid":2113360,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【正視聽】成班人喺咪推緊個膠post【我瀨咗嘢呀屌】","createTime":"2020-07-18T05:18:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-18T16:11:55.000Z","uid":259088,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"35a61bffdd43a476e7ba8e6070089942027dead1","tid":2113360,"uid":259088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T05:18:55.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">香港人 要推嘅 <br />\n就請你哋全世界幫手推個正常post救香港啦！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">保安局發出左超過20萬張豁免強制檢疫</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2102947/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2102947/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n請大家支持廣傳消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔自救大家玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">我哋可以做咩嘢？</span></span></strong><br />\n1.話比身邊嘅人知香港有個後門大量吸收潛在冇病症感染者及傳播者。<br />\n<br />\n2.呼籲身邊所有人戴口罩，特別係果班唔肯帶嘅中年人<br />\n<br />\n3.如果身邊有料，可以報上傳媒比如蘋果。<br />\n例如喺之前post有其他人話知道：<br />\n灣仔入境個邊D移民公司而家當免檢疫証明係生意咁做，搵班阿姐派傳單幫人攪。<br />\n每日中港司機都幾千人出出入入。<br />\n<br />\n4.煲大件事！比全世界多D人知道，只有多D人覺醒，知道個政府係棄全香港巿民安危不顧，先會爭取到更多人企係我哋呢邊，同我哋一齊抗疫！<br />\n<br />\n兄弟姊妹各自爬山 他日平安相聚<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b18ef2be7da5621b26dbfef2ad84f5a8adbe6909","tid":2113360,"uid":96091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T05:20:12.000Z","msg":"連登多戇鳩"},{"pid":"6fc0316740503add9f9971f861cc1371745f2733","tid":2113360,"uid":259088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b18ef2be7da5621b26dbfef2ad84f5a8adbe6909","tid":2113360,"uid":96091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T05:20:12.000Z","msg":"連登多戇鳩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T05:28:04.000Z","msg":"係成個討論區比人騎劫左姐"},{"pid":"c3f76f07b1f8340c9e9730e769d5dba83749180c","tid":2113360,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T16:11:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}